                    <td><strong>Duster</strong></td>
                    <td>8-10pm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Fri Jan 28</td>
                    <td><strong>Horse Jumper of Love</strong></td>
                    <td>8-10pm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Fri Feb 4</td>
                    <td><strong>Yves Tumor</strong></td>
                    <td>8-10pm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Fri Feb 11</td>
